sinimR 0.1.3
  • Reference

Get a SINIM variable data in a specific year as a data frame

Source: R/getsinimr.R
getsinimr.Rd

Get a SINIM variable data in a specific year as a data frame

getsinimr(var, year, moncorr = T)

Arguments

var

variable code
year

year
moncorr

A logical value indicating the use of monetary correction

Value

data frame with data for the requested variable over time

Examples

getsinimr(880, 2015)
